lert triggered from Singapore node.\n\n[MOM #1 - 2026-05-15 07:46]\nStatus updated from MOM review.\n\n[MOM #1 - 2026-05-15 07:46]\nStatus updated from MOM review.\n\n[MOM #1 - 2026-05-15 07:46]\nStatus updated from MOM review.\n\n[MOM #1 - 2026-05-15 07:46]\nStatus updated from MOM review.','completed','critical','2026-05-08 20:35:11','2026-05-08 20:06:11','2026-05-15 07:46:27'),(24,1,1,NULL,'Cloud backup checksum mismatch','Need manual checksum validation.','on_hold','high','2026-05-09 03:26:11','2026-05-08 08:26:11','2026-06-24 09:31:44'),(25,1,1,NULL,'Expired SSL cleanup pending','Old certificates still detected on edge node.','pending','low','2026-05-10 20:26:11','2026-05-06 20:26:11','2026-05-08 20:26:11'),(28,1,1,'Administrator','test notif','','completed','medium',NULL,'2026-05-26 09:13:42','2026-05-26 19:32:29'),(29,1,1,'Administrator','test browser notif','','completed','medium',NULL,'2026-05-26 19:32:01','2026-05-26 19:32:22');
